headline: Visa launches Click to Pay in Hong Kong with ZA Bank, the first issuing bank in Asia Pacific
summary: Visa, a global leader in digital payments, today announced a significant advancement that will transform the eCommerce experience. Hong Kong's first and largest digital bank[1], ZA Bank, pioneers Click to Pay, enabling cardholders to complete online transactions in seconds without the need for manual card entry. ZA Bank is the first card issuing bank to enable Visa Click to Pay in Hong Kong and across Asia Pacific, with 11 more markets to follow.
